      <h4 class="bline"><span>热点</span></h4> 
      <ul class="pic clear">
       <li><a title="余文乐身高" target="_blank" href="/star/star-84270.html"><span>余文乐身高</span><img width="140" height="105" alt="余文乐身高" src="http://pic.lutoo.org/150608/2-15060Q52P0P8-lp.jpg" /></a></li> 
